tables.description: This table has basic information about a customer, as well as some derived facts based on a customer's orders
tables.name: customers

fields.description: This is a unique identifier for a customer
fields.name: customer_id

fields.description: Date (UTC) of a customer's first order
fields.name: first_order

fields.description: Date (UTC) of a customer's most recent order
fields.name: most_recent_order

fields.description: Count of the number of orders a customer has placed
fields.name: number_of_orders

fields.description: Total value (AUD) of a customer's orders
fields.name: customer_lifetime_value

tables.description: This table has basic information about orders, as well as some derived facts based on payments
tables.name: orders

fields.description: This is a unique identifier for an order
fields.name: order_id

fields.description: Foreign key to the customers table
fields.name: customer_id

target.description: This is a unique identifier for a customer
target.name: customer_id

fields.description: Date (UTC) that the order was placed
fields.name: order_date

fields.description: Amount of the order (AUD) paid for by credit card
fields.name: credit_card_amount

fields.description: Amount of the order (AUD) paid for by coupon
fields.name: coupon_amount

fields.description: Amount of the order (AUD) paid for by bank transfer
fields.name: bank_transfer_amount

fields.description: Amount of the order (AUD) paid for by gift card
fields.name: gift_card_amount

tables.caveats: Some facts are derived from payments

tables.description: This table has basic information about payments
tables.name: transactions

fields.description: This is a unique identifier for a payment
fields.name: payment_id

fields.description: Foreign key to the orders table
fields.name: order_id

target.description: This is a unique identifier for an order
target.name: order_id
